This is app for Android, created to help students in preparation for entrance exams.
With this app we get 3rd place in All-Ukrainian student contest “Golden Byte” in nomination “Mobile Technologies”.

Now application is in beta-testing.
Latest version you may download here pitest.org.ua/android/TestTerra.apk
There are only one subject ( Ukrainian language ), which includes 264 multiple-choice tests provided by friendly site http://lvtest.org.ua/

Release is planned for the beginning of November, 2012. See you soon!